				\begin{document}$${\text{O}}_{2}^{ - }$$\end{document}), and singlet oxygen O2(a1Δg). Because of the short life time of the most above-mentioned species outside the plasma applicator far from the plasma generator, the objects are sterilized by ozone (O3) since its minimum lifetime is rather long (some minutes). The microwave method of oxygen plasma generation is the best for the energy-efficient production of ozone.
